        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-4205003"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>Adding 8SP to consider Project Management and high level architecture effort.</p>
        </td></tr>
                <tr id="comment-header-4202864"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            Comment by  
                                                        <a class="user-hover" rel="avima01" id="word_commented_avima01" href="https://jira.safeway.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=avima01">Amrendra Vimal</a>
                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">20/Feb/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-4202864"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p><b>Estimation</b> :</p>

<p>Key Points considered(Assumptions) for estimations:<br/>
&#8211; Associate Details needs to be captured.<br/>
&#8211; Privacy Conscent Capture.<br/>
&#8211; Post Capture Cancellation Out of scope.<br/>
&#8211; Auto Cancellation or pre-order cancellation in scope.<br/>
&#8211; Slot validation will remain as is what we do for MTO-Kiosk.<br/>
&#8211; Orders will be taken as a seperate order other than regular ecom Order and will be published to DOMS.<br/>
&#8211; Payments or allocations would not be captured.<br/>
&#8211; Tax, Offers, EPE, FAS integration would not be there for such orders.<br/>
&#8211; This would also have ticketing integration.<br/>
&#8211; These order can't be edited</p>

<p>Note: Post order capture no changes discussed for fulfillment re-pricing flow.</p>

<p><b>Resource - Total  Sprints - 4 ( 32 SP)</b> <br/>
Service → 4 sprints (0.5 Sprint Spike, 2.5 Sprint Dev, .5 Sprint Auto, 0.5 Sprint QA) - 4 sprints)</p>
<ul class="alternate" type="square">
	<li>3 services impacted(Cart, Checkout, Order)</li>
</ul>


<p><b>Parallel: 2 Sprints</b></p>

        </td></tr>
                <tr id="comment-header-4197490"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            Comment by  
                                                        <a class="user-hover" rel="avima01" id="word_commented_avima01" href="https://jira.safeway.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=avima01">Amrendra Vimal</a>
                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">18/Feb/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-4197490"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            <p>Note: Post order Capture - Cancel Order is not handled at Cart &amp; Checkout end, our estimations(WIP) would be excluding line item 7. <br/>
